sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant API as Backend API
  participant Auth as Auth Use-Case
  participant Repo as User Repository

  User->>API: POST /auth/register
  API->>Auth: RegisterUser.execute
  Auth->>Repo: findByEmail
  Repo-->>Auth: none
  Auth->>Repo: save(User)
  Auth-->>API: user id + email
  API-->>User: 201 Created

  User->>API: POST /auth/login
  API->>Auth: LoginUser.execute
  Auth->>Repo: findByEmail
  Repo-->>Auth: user
  Auth-->>API: accessToken
  API-->>User: 201 Created
